5
00:01:10,239 --> 00:01:11,400
The comic book is in the office.

6
00:01:11,519 --> 00:01:12,359
Go get it yourself.

7
00:01:16,400 --> 00:01:17,200
Ke Yu'ang,

8
00:01:18,079 --> 00:01:19,480
