15
00:01:41,120 --> 00:01:42,480
but more importantly,

16
00:01:42,760 --> 00:01:44,439
we need to catch the spy Lin Chuyi

17
00:01:44,640 --> 00:01:45,760
and bring her to justice.

18
00:01:46,319 --> 00:01:47,120
Yes, sir.

19
00:02:07,680 --> 00:02:08,520
Great.

20
00:02:10,199 --> 00:02:11,639
I can clear the name

21
00:02:11,840 --> 00:02:13,039
