27
00:02:41,919 --> 00:02:42,639
Where is she?

28
00:02:42,639 --> 00:02:44,759
Jiang Xun was kidnapped in Lin Tianlu's villa.

29
00:02:44,759 --> 00:02:45,560
Requesting backup.

30
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:46,840
Okay, I got it.

31
00:02:46,840 --> 00:02:48,680
We're on our way to assist you.

32
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:51,599
Let's go.

33
00:02:51,599 --> 00:02:52,400
Roger that.

34
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:00,120
Jiang Xun.

35
00:03:00,439 --> 00:03:01,560
You just got back to Rongzhou.

36
00:03:01,719 --> 00:03:03,599
The first thing you did was not going home.

37
00:03:04,159 --> 00:03:05,919
You brought me here to...

38
00:03:08,159 --> 00:03:09,360
Deputy Shen.

39
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:11,120
The game is over.

40
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:13,639
Hand over the cryptographic key,

41
00:03:14,319 --> 00:03:15,240
