42
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:23,439
Do you think I'll tell you?

43
00:03:25,039 --> 00:03:25,840
Lin Chuyi,

44
00:03:26,759 --> 00:03:27,840
I always thought

45
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:29,599
