53
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:44,199
Your self-righteousness.

54
00:03:44,479 --> 00:03:45,719
To be honest,

55
00:03:48,560 --> 00:03:49,599
I'm not

56
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:51,719
