65
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:30,040
You did the same.

66
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:32,360
You used me.

67
00:04:32,519 --> 00:04:33,800
And I used you.

68
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:35,720
Now we're even.

69
00:04:36,879 --> 00:04:39,319
You set me up,

70
00:04:39,720 --> 00:04:41,600
but my goal

71
00:04:41,759 --> 00:04:44,319
