72
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:46,920
Jiang Xun!

73
00:04:47,199 --> 00:04:48,000
Shen Shutu!

74
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:49,160
Don't touch her.

75
00:04:49,399 --> 00:04:50,319
Hand over the cryptographic key,

76
00:04:50,439 --> 00:04:51,759
