81
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:01,000
I'll write it.

82
00:05:01,360 --> 00:05:02,160
No.

83
00:05:02,360 --> 00:05:03,759
Don't be fooled by her, Jiang Xun.

84
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:09,040
Don't be fooled by her.

85
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:16,879
No!

86
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:26,120
The key is correct.

87
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:28,120
Good.

88
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:30,240
Send the key to the superior immediately.

89
00:05:30,759 --> 00:05:32,920
As long as this file is sent out,

90
00:05:33,399 --> 00:05:34,639
I will win.

91
00:05:34,879 --> 00:05:35,560
Move!

92
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:49,800
Don't move!

93
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:50,839
Don't move!

94
00:05:50,839 --> 00:05:51,839
Don't move!

95
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:53,279
Don't move!

96
00:05:55,040 --> 00:05:56,480
Don't move!

97
00:05:57,519 --> 00:05:58,439
Don't move!

98
00:05:58,839 --> 00:05:59,639
Where's Lin Chuyi?

99
00:05:59,639 --> 00:06:00,279
Over there!

100
00:06:02,480 --> 00:06:03,519
Police! Freeze!

101
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:05,959
Protect Jiang Xun!

102
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:07,519
Protect Jiang Xun!

103
00:06:07,519 --> 00:06:08,040
Yes, sir!

104
00:06:28,959 --> 00:06:29,519
Feng!

105
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:31,240
Feng, are you okay?

106
00:06:31,240 --> 00:06:31,680
I'm fine.

107
00:06:31,720 --> 00:06:32,360
Leave me alone.

108
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:33,319
Go after Lin Chuyi.

109
00:06:33,759 --> 00:06:34,079
Hurry.

110
00:06:37,680 --> 00:06:39,399
Lin Chuyi, put the gun down.

111
00:06:40,439 --> 00:06:41,279
Put the gun down.

112
00:06:41,639 --> 00:06:42,439
Lin Chuyi.

113
00:06:43,040 --> 00:06:43,839
Put the gun down.

114
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:52,839
Lin Chuyi.

115
00:06:55,839 --> 00:06:56,639
Put the gun down.

116
00:06:57,040 --> 00:06:58,000
It's all over.

117
00:07:00,279 --> 00:07:01,480
So you lured me to the museum

118
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:02,319
