120
00:07:05,319 --> 00:07:06,360
I've given you a chance.

121
00:07:07,560 --> 00:07:08,439
Really?

122
00:07:09,560 --> 00:07:11,079
I had no choice.

123
00:08:31,399 --> 00:08:32,200
Shen Shutu.

124
00:08:33,159 --> 00:08:35,320
You finally came back.

125
00:08:37,080 --> 00:08:38,360
I've always been here.

126
00:08:40,120 --> 00:08:41,080
I'm sorry

127
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:42,279
