129
00:09:04,559 --> 00:09:05,879
[In the new era,]

130
00:09:05,879 --> 00:09:08,240
[the loyalty of national security has never faded.]

131
00:09:08,759 --> 00:09:10,879
[The spirit of responsibility is passed down from generation to generation.]

132
00:09:11,120 --> 00:09:13,919
[Our officers fulfill their missions with their lives,]

133
00:09:14,120 --> 00:09:15,720
[building a monument with their passion.]

134
00:09:15,759 --> 00:09:18,120
[They stick to their original aspirations in the storm,]

135
00:09:18,320 --> 00:09:20,279
[and carry heavy burdens in silence.]

136
00:09:20,279 --> 00:09:21,519
Why are you nervous?

137
00:09:23,399 --> 00:09:26,720
It's my first time attending such a solemn and serious meeting.

138
00:09:27,679 --> 00:09:30,200
This is a secret commendation meeting

139
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:31,399
