140
00:09:31,399 --> 00:09:32,320
Smile.

141
00:09:32,320 --> 00:09:34,360
[In the Jiaotu No.1 espionage case,]

142
00:09:34,519 --> 00:09:35,960
[Ms. Jiang Xun,]

143
00:09:35,960 --> 00:09:38,120
[with the ordinary identity of a cultural relics restorer,]

144
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:39,879
[with her keen observation]

145
00:09:39,879 --> 00:09:41,360
[and strong sense of responsibility,]

146
00:09:41,519 --> 00:09:43,320
[not only helped capture the spy,]

147
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:44,919
[but also uncovered the historical truth,]

148
00:09:45,039 --> 00:09:47,679
[and carried forward the patriotic spirit of her ancestors.]

149
00:09:47,679 --> 00:09:49,080
[She has proved that ordinary people]

150
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:50,919
[can also fulfill their missions]

151
00:09:50,919 --> 00:09:52,279
[and protect national security.]

152
00:09:53,559 --> 00:09:55,039
[Let's welcome Ms. Jiang Xun.]

153
00:09:59,240 --> 00:10:01,440
[Now, on behalf of Rongzhou Security,]

154
00:10:01,440 --> 00:10:03,639
[I'll present the award to Ms. Jiang Xun.]

155
00:10:24,399 --> 00:10:25,200
You've done a great job.

156
00:10:25,200 --> 00:10:25,879
Thank you.

157
00:10:26,399 --> 00:10:27,960
You deserve this recognition.

158
00:10:36,960 --> 00:10:37,759
