161
00:10:44,759 --> 00:10:46,480
From now on, no matter what,

162
00:10:48,080 --> 00:10:49,519
I'll be as brave as her.

163
00:10:58,639 --> 00:10:59,440
Miss Jiang,

164
00:11:01,120 --> 00:11:03,679
this is the handwritten draft of Wu Shixuan,

165
00:11:03,679 --> 00:11:05,279
the head of the Rongzhou intelligence group.

166
00:11:05,559 --> 00:11:06,840
It was badly damaged before,

167
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:08,120
but I restored it myself.

168
00:11:08,519 --> 00:11:10,679
It details their operation routes.

169
00:11:11,440 --> 00:11:14,440
After Wu Shixuan and Jiang Chihui sacrificed,

170
00:11:14,519 --> 00:11:15,879
my great-grandmother Song Jin'an

171
00:11:15,879 --> 00:11:17,480
negotiated with the Japanese army secretly

172
00:11:17,679 --> 00:11:18,919
and died alone.

173
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:20,799
I'm grateful to Mr. Wu

174
00:11:20,799 --> 00:11:22,279
for letting me restore it,

175
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:24,519
and give my great-grandmother justice

176
00:11:24,519 --> 00:11:25,759
and fairness.

177
00:11:25,960 --> 00:11:27,240
The rumors and opinions

178
00:11:27,240 --> 00:11:29,519
about Miss Jiang and the Jiang family

179
00:11:29,559 --> 00:11:30,960
are heartbreaking.

180
00:11:31,039 --> 00:11:34,159
It's unacceptable to smear the martyrs

181
00:11:34,159 --> 00:11:35,240
and their families.

182
00:11:35,440 --> 00:11:37,840
I'm willing to donate this manuscript to the museum.

183
00:11:37,840 --> 00:11:40,440
The deeds of heroes should not be misunderstood and buried.

184
00:11:40,759 --> 00:11:43,679
We will report this story truthfully.

185
00:11:43,679 --> 00:11:45,559
Finally, I would like to ask Miss Jiang.

186
00:11:45,639 --> 00:11:47,639
Does the dragon and phoenix jade pendant you donated

187
00:11:47,639 --> 00:11:48,960
