188
00:11:54,120 --> 00:11:55,279
It symbolizes good fortune

189
00:11:55,960 --> 00:11:59,639
and love can be conveyed through time and space.

190
00:12:03,399 --> 00:12:04,039
Also,

191
00:12:04,039 --> 00:12:05,360
we hope the public

192
00:12:05,360 --> 00:12:06,960
can pay attention to

193
00:12:06,960 --> 00:12:08,679
the joint exhibition

194
00:12:08,679 --> 00:12:11,039
