195
00:12:11,240 --> 00:12:13,039
and actively participate in anti-espionage.

196
00:12:13,240 --> 00:12:16,679
Please follow the official WeChat account of the Security Bureau.

197
00:12:17,960 --> 00:12:18,519
Okay.

198
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:22,159
Thank you, Miss Jiang.

199
00:12:22,399 --> 00:12:24,960
