205
00:12:33,080 --> 00:12:34,960
Have we met before?

206
00:12:35,600 --> 00:12:38,279
Honestly, I feel the same way.

207
00:12:38,679 --> 00:12:40,759
Miss Jiang comes from a scholarly family.

208
00:12:40,919 --> 00:12:42,799
How could you have met a wanderer like me?

209
00:12:43,159 --> 00:12:45,000
The Young Master of Shen Group

210
00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:46,759
