220
00:13:04,600 --> 00:13:05,679
After the exhibition,

221
00:13:05,679 --> 00:13:07,320
more people will know about this history,

222
00:13:07,320 --> 00:13:08,279
and the deeds

223
00:13:08,279 --> 00:13:09,279
of these unsung heroes.

224
00:13:09,960 --> 00:13:10,919
That's right.

225
00:13:11,200 --> 00:13:12,679
With more people on our side,

226
00:13:12,679 --> 00:13:14,399
