231
00:13:23,039 --> 00:13:24,320
Wasn't that well said?

232
00:13:24,519 --> 00:13:25,759
Very good.

233
00:13:26,039 --> 00:13:27,759
Funny and romantic.

234
00:13:27,759 --> 00:13:29,080
And...

235
00:13:30,399 --> 00:13:31,600
And?

236
00:13:32,159 --> 00:13:34,120
I think I heard a hint of

237
00:13:34,120 --> 00:13:35,360
