Love can transcend time and space.

241
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:45,000
I think so too.

242
00:13:45,399 --> 00:13:47,240
Because no matter what universe,

243
00:13:47,519 --> 00:13:48,440
I love you.

244
00:13:56,039 --> 00:13:56,840
Okay.

245
00:13:57,320 --> 00:13:59,480
