255
00:15:19,559 --> 00:15:20,480
National security,

256
00:15:20,480 --> 00:15:21,639
everything for the people,

257
00:15:21,879 --> 00:15:23,279
everything relies on the people.

258
00:15:23,759 --> 00:15:24,559
[In the drama,]

259
00:15:24,919 --> 00:15:26,000
[the national security agency]

260
00:15:26,000 --> 00:15:28,320
[held an internal commendation meeting for Jiang Xun,]

261
00:15:28,879 --> 00:15:29,639
[to pay tribute to her]

262
00:15:29,639 --> 00:15:32,240
